# Iced UI Patterns

## Application Structure
- `ui::run()`: `iced::application(state, update, view).title(...).subscription(...).run()`
- State: `MainWindow` with `Default` impl
- Update: `fn update(&mut self, msg: Message) -> Task<Message>`
- View: `fn view(&self) -> Element<'_, Message>`

## Subcomponents
- Struct per window/panel with `view()` returning `Element<'_, Message>`
- Component constructor: `Component::new(Length::Fill, Length::Fixed(50_f32))`
- Use `components::rack()` and `components::module_slot()` for layout

## Styling
- `threads/ui/style/mod.rs`: Theme functions `rack`, `module_slot`, `module`, `display`, `control`, `label`
- Color constants at top: `LIGHT_GRAY`, `DARK_GRAY`, `CASING_BLACK`, etc.
- `color!(0x968B86)` for hex colors

## Subscriptions
- Combine: `Subscription::batch(vec![window_events, tick, data_change])`
- Custom: implement `Recipe` with `hash()` and `stream()` for async sources (e.g., flume receiver)
